Package fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.formattools.rtf Description

Provides all classes and methods to de-encapsulate HTML and text from RTF.

Conform with MSDN directives to de-encapsulate HTML from RTF https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ee159984(v=exchg.80).aspx
